song.title: Do You Wanna Dance With Me?
song.info:
From D Fast's album, [url=http://www.dfastmusic.net/planetboogie/]Planet Boogie[/url]
Lyrics: Baby! Baby, baby, yeah!
Do you wanna dance with me? Do you wanna dance with me? I wanna dance with you, baby I wanna dance with you
I wanna watch you move, move it now, move it now
Do you wanna dance with me?
I know you, You know me, I know what you want from me.
Do you wanna dance with me? (I wanna dance with you) Do you wanna dance with me?
